    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Indian carpet and textile style that is an interpretation of Turkoman style from the historic West Turkestani region, typically with an overall repeating geometric medallion design.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
